data.name: FleetSetupWizardIntroductionText
data.value:
Before you can work with Route Planner, we'll need some information about your fleet. This short wizard will set up a new project with your basic fleet details. You can add or edit details later.
Step 1: Enter Start, End and Renewal depots.
Step 2: Enter route information including vehicles, drivers and some constraints.
Step 3: Optionally, import orders from a file or database.
